MockFS is a test-obsessed library for mocking out the entire file system. It provides mock objects that clone the functionality of File, FileUtils, Dir, and other in-Ruby file-access libraries.

http://rubyforge.org/projects/mockfs/

REQUIREMENTS:
* Extensions ( http://extensions.rubyforge.org/ )

INSTALLATION:
As root, run "./install.rb", which will copy the Ruby files into the right
subdirectory. You can run "./install.rb --help" for information.
